程序包 org.apache.log

类 LogEvent

java.lang.Object
org.apache.log.LogEvent
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
@Deprecated public final class LogEvent extends Object implements Serializable
已过时。
Will be dropped in 3.3
This class encapsulates each individual log event. LogEvents usually originate at a Logger and are routed to LogTargets.
